summary: ok so can i say how much i loved this pair. like gosh, why did the writers hate this pair so much? they had a great meet cute,...
caption: ok so can i say how much i loved this pair. like gosh, why did the writers hate this pair so much? they had a great meet cute, andi had told jonah that she was no longer obsessed with him and that she was free, andi and walker painted a mural together, but andi suddenly became re infatuated with jonah via a song and then those two started dating AGAIN. and then by the time summer was over, andi was over jonah. and then meanwhile they had walker start “dating” buffy, someone he interacted with twice. three times? i just really miss wandi and it sucks that we’ll probably never see them interact the way they used to. RIP WANDI. rest in peace
